{"tid":306821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［後悔太遲］調查：6成英國民眾想保留歐盟身分","createTime":"2017-07-03T00:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T05:03:22.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da443eb56bf2cc3495d665dba294b77c4935c0b4","tid":306821,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:30:01.000Z","msg":"後悔脫歐了？ 調查：6成英國民眾想保留歐盟身分<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕英國脫歐公投去年6月過關，不過倫敦政治經濟學院（London School of Economics, LSE）發布的最新民調卻指出，有高達6成英國人想要繼續保有歐盟公民身分。<br />\n根據英國《衛報》報導，倫敦政經學院調查指出，2000名受訪者中，有6成想保留歐盟公民身分，另外有大量受訪者願意花大筆款項，以繼續在歐盟生活、工作、學習、旅遊等。其中尤其以18至24歲年輕受訪者比例最高，高達85%想要保持歐盟公民身分，住在倫敦的受訪者也有8成表明想留歐。<br />\n主導研究的倫敦政經學院歐洲政治學教授布魯特（Michael Bruter）表示，這顯示年輕人失去對未來前景至關重要的權利感到「非常不開心」，他們願意付出遠超過水平的高額費用來保留這些權利。<br />\n調查指出，為了保有歐盟公民資格，他們願意支付的平均金額高於400英鎊（約新台幣15000元），讓他們可以自由進出、工作、旅行、讀書或居住歐盟各國。<br />\n另外調查也顯示，在選舉制度方面，有25％受訪者希望能保持現狀，僅10％的人贊同政府撤除歐盟公民在地方選舉中的投票權。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2118767\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2118767&d=zvgcQPVlc%2F91PamQ6ZY%2FGMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=72b61393\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2118767&h=d6d7290d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2118767</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/082725_de00246a0299d319612ab533c269091d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F082725_de00246a0299d319612ab533c269091d.jpg&h=e6246293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國攪脫歐公投本來諗住大歐盟，<br />\n所以都無宣傳脫歐是什麼<br />\n好多投讚成既純粹貪新鮮，對歐盟一知半解<br />\n面家後悔太遲"},{"pid":"3dddaceeca32362738390b2649b5e37d6daf9286","tid":306821,"uid":50663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:32:16.000Z","msg":"好似係老一輩唔想留"},{"pid":"6cca1d09c0f880d71b70e4d417733fe9343deba7","tid":306821,"uid":22378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:34:23.000Z","msg":"倫敦本身都係投留歐<br />\n咁訪問倫敦市民當然係留歐居多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb879be9ac16c40ec1d981efcad2fe04077528d","tid":306821,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:46:11.000Z","msg":"遲早被左膠害死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5a4ba493c869f5cbb7fbc5edcaf1221da5ddaf","tid":306821,"uid":1900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:48:11.000Z","msg":"依d調查出黎個結果有誤導性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc917f67728fde6a4a3eea17fe89ca276e42072","tid":306821,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:49:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>倫敦本身都係投留歐<br />\n咁訪問倫敦市民當然係留歐居多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊度有寫淨係訪問倫敦市民？"},{"pid":"d9d6a83e3dd02eca2bcfafbd2d2aac4f54042e44","tid":306821,"uid":45518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:51:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>倫敦本身都係投留歐<br />\n咁訪問倫敦市民當然係留歐居多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊度有寫淨係訪問倫敦市民？</blockquote><br />\n只係話當中嘅倫敦受訪者有八成想留歐，六成應該係指全國"},{"pid":"5b046f838ff90eb0a2682aeffcd19e2916ad23b9","tid":306821,"uid":59690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:56:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>倫敦本身都係投留歐<br />\n咁訪問倫敦市民當然係留歐居多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLse搞唔一定只揾london住喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ab608249171570e46cd212f12c0c51e223862e","tid":306821,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:51:01.000Z","msg":"聽到要付1000億歐元分手費先識驚"},{"pid":"1359c1586e3f5aa7dadd9ecc3ce458fab97f3315","tid":306821,"uid":98692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"